OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fquite cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with some showery rain. Some
OL,8,Fdrier and clearer spells developing
OL,9,Ftowards morning. Windy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA mostly dry start with some
OL,12,Fbright spells. Rain spreads in from
OL,13,Fthe west through the morning,
OL,14,Foccasionally heavy. Drier in east.
OL,15,FClear spells and showers in evening.
OL,16,FBreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
