OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry
OL,6,Fstart Friday but chance of rain for a
OL,7,Ftime in the middle of the day. Dry and
OL,8,Fbright for most of Saturday, rain
OL,9,Flater. Cloudy, breezy, patchy rain
OL,10,FSunday.
